OperationListResult Class

Definition

Result of the request to list SQL operations. It contains a list of operations and a URL link to get the next set of results.

In this Article

public class OperationListResult
Inheritance
Object
OperationListResult

Constructors

OperationListResult()

Initializes a new instance of the OperationListResult class.
OperationListResult(IList<Operation>, String)

Initializes a new instance of the OperationListResult class.

Properties

NextLink

Gets or sets URL to get the next set of operation list results if there are any.
Value

Gets or sets list of SQL operations supported by the SQL resource provider.
